.TH "LIGHTNING-WALLET-EXPORT-BACKUP" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-wallet-export-backup \- copy wallet database to a backup file
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning wallet-export-backup
.I wallet_name
.RI [ dest_dir ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Copies the wallet SQLite database to a timestamped file in
.IR dest_dir
(default: current directory).
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"status":"exported","path":"<file>","wallet":"<name>"}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-wallet-backup-verify (1),
.BR lightning-wallet-export-json (1)
